{"tid":1908150,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[法治] 仲有冇人記得用胸襲警案？","createTime":"2020-03-03T05:31:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T05:36:17.000Z","uid":15010,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"21e836c8645b608a3e9ef3c82c3edcdc1fbccb7b","tid":1908150,"uid":15010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T05:31:51.000Z","msg":"背景:<br />\n<br />\n去年（2015年）3月示威者吳麗英參與「光復元朗」行動，吳與另3名示威者及後分別被控阻差辦公及襲警罪。去年審訊時，吳麗英指案發時遭警察非禮，並被男警從後推跌至滿面披血鼻骨骨折，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>惟裁判官裁定吳實是以胸撞警，裁定她襲警罪成</strong></span>，判監3個半月。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3HHqvc3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3HHqvc3.gif&h=906d4624&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n件事發生係2015年，立法會選舉係2016年，而dead body講呢番說話既時候係2016年2月21日。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/新東補選-楊岳橋-如有人想搞司法系統-over-my-dead-body/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%96%B0%E6%9D%B1%E8%A3%9C%E9%81%B8-%E6%A5%8A%E5%B2%B3%E6%A9%8B-%E5%A6%82%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E6%83%B3%E6%90%9E%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1-over-my-dead-body%2F&d=HqwfJ7ndl2RLmQbQQ2LVpoVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=122ac7bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%96%B0%E6%9D%B1%E8%A3%9C%E9%81%B8-%E6%A5%8A%E5%B2%B3%E6%A9%8B-%E5%A6%82%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E6%83%B3%E6%90%9E%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1-over-my-dead-body%2F&h=a4c8b7cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/新東補選-楊岳橋-如有人想搞司法系統-over-my-dead-body/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然之後女文員提岀上訴，但高等法院只係就判刑上訴得直，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">換句話講，即係依然係被定罪</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n立場新聞link: <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/以胸襲警案-4被告定罪上訴被駁回-惟判刑上訴得直/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E4%BB%A5%E8%83%B8%E8%A5%B2%E8%AD%A6%E6%A1%88-4%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E5%AE%9A%E7%BD%AA%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4%E8%A2%AB%E9%A7%81%E5%9B%9E-%E6%83%9F%E5%88%A4%E5%88%91%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4%E5%BE%97%E7%9B%B4%2F&d=HqwfJ7ndl2RLmQbQQ2LVpoVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=bf622d06\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E4%BB%A5%E8%83%B8%E8%A5%B2%E8%AD%A6%E6%A1%88-4%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E5%AE%9A%E7%BD%AA%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4%E8%A2%AB%E9%A7%81%E5%9B%9E-%E6%83%9F%E5%88%A4%E5%88%91%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4%E5%BE%97%E7%9B%B4%2F&h=12316703\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/以胸襲警案-4被告定罪上訴被駁回-惟判刑上訴得直/</a><br />\n<br />\n總結:<br />\n<br />\n有好多手足已經因爲呢個腐爛既制度而入獄<br />\n尋晚有個post有手足連女朋友都冇埋<br />\n亦有好多依家正係，或者將會因為咁<br />\n而面臨巨大既財政困難，甚至係心理壓力<br />\n<br />\n而另一邊箱有人不斷作奸犯科、濫用權力<br />\n甚至係有意不作為都可以毫無後果<br />\n更甚者，濫捕、濫告、酷刑、恐嚇都冇事<br />\n告手足用重罪、告奶共深藍就用輕d既罪<br />\n已經唔講裁判官d所謂判刑理由同個人comments<br />\n<br />\n經過咁多事件，前人又好，過去8個月又好<br />\n想問下公民黨尤其係deadbody<br />\n幾時先肯承認法治已死<br />\n仲要係已經死去一段時間<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">國際上黎講，呢d野律師黨講一句<br />\n好過我地講十句</span>"},{"pid":"bf67064f4f6201045e97ddf3b5eaef1c917ae114","tid":1908150,"uid":303311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T05:36:17.000Z","msg":"我記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}